title: MONDAY - Drew Brees dominates Tom Brady 2020
itunes:title: MONDAY - Drew Brees dominates Tom Brady 2020
description:
Sunday night football saw Drew Brees and the Saints totally dominate Tom Brady and the Buccaneers (0:07). Josh Allen thrusting his name into the the MVP race (1:26) as he tops Russell Wilson and the Seahawks. Hear what Wilson had to say about the loss (1:55). It was a matchup of two young guns (2:51) as Tua Tagovailoa went up against Kyler Murray and the Cardinals. Ben Roethlisberger and the Steelers doing something no Pittsburgh team has ever done (3:22), and we have a preview of the Monday night matchup (4:22) between the Patriots and Jets
